# Read End User License Agreement Information

**Web Service Endpoint**

Get the custom end user license agreement associated with an app, and the territories it applies to.

## Reading EULA and Listing Territories

- **Read the End User License Agreement Information of an App**: Get the custom end user license agreement (EULA) for a specific app and the territories where the agreement applies.
- **List All Territories for an End User License Agreement**: List all the App Store territories to which a specific custom app license agreement applies.
- **GET /v1/endUserLicenseAgreements/{id}/relationships/territories**
